Usage: AWAYT time_in_minutes
  Sets time before you're automatically set away if idle

  Default auto-away time is 10. Setting this to 0 disables auto-away.

See also:
  PLAYBACK
  REMLOG
  SETAWAY
  SETBACK
  SHOWAWAY
